		<h1 class="banner">for every family without books.</h1>


		<section class="video" >
			<iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/sMAvF67CdUI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
		</section>


		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>The problem</h2>
		</div>		
		<section class="the-problem pure-g"> 
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
				<div class="text">
					<h2>The problem</h2>
					<p>
						Poorer kids are set up to fail before they even start preschool. By age three, they’ve heard <span>30 million fewer words</span> than wealthier kids— a word-gap that stunts early brain growth.
					</p>
					<p>
						Books get families talking, but 1 billion families just don’t have access to any books or Internet. 
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="girl pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
				<img src="/images/modules/sad-girl.png" alt="">
			</div>
			
		</section>
		
		<div class="divider"><div></div></div>
			

			
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>The product</h2>
		</div>		
		<section class="the-product pure-g"> 

			<div class="phone pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
				<img src="/images/modules/phone.png" alt="">
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
				<div class="text">
					<h2>The product</h2>
					<p>
						
						But 6 billion do have mobile phones. We send illustrated children’s stories by text message and messaging apps to get families talking face-to-face. 

					</p>
					<p>
						And it’s <span>300x cheaper</span> than just shipping paperbacks.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			
		</section>

		<div class="divider"><div></div></div>
	
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Where we're going</h2>
		</div>		
		<section class="join-us pure-g">
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
				<div class="v-align">
					<div class="text">
						<h2>The progress</h2>
						<p>
				As part of a $24M grant with the US government, we’re piloting with tens of thousands of families.
						</p>
						<p>
				And with our first families, StoryTime increased nightly reading <span>by 160%</span>.  
						</p>

					</div>

				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="partners pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
					<img src="/images/modules/partners.png" alt="">
			</div>

		</section>

		<div class="divider"><div></div></div>

		
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>The people</h2>
		</div>		
		<section class="the-product pure-g"> 

			<div class="prize pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
				<img src="/images/modules/Thorne_Prize.png" alt="">
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-2">
				<div class="text">
					<h2>The people</h2>
					<p>
						
						We’re a Yale team of developers and former Head Start preschool teachers. 

					</p>

					<p>We built StoryTime for our class’s families at Martinez Head Start. Now, we’re solving the word gap at scale. </p>

				</div>
			</div>
			
			
		</section>

